"msg":"派系鬥爭<br />\n<br />\n編輯係江派, 主筆係習派"},{"pid":"0405438a00bfc20517043536e73b8520960d6671","tid":1939024,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b72735f6b3f9dadb009eebc418fea97df73aad7f","tid":1939024,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"反正我就相信了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"你唔信都大把人信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}